=== Noun ===
'''bat''' (''plural'' '''bats''')

# a small, [[nocturnal]], flying [[mammal]]. Bats are able to find their way around at night by [[sonar]], making squeaks and listening to the [[echo]] with their very sensitive ears.  ([[w:Bat|Wikipedia:Bat]])
# a sort of hitting club made of wood or aluminum used in sports such as [[baseball]], [[softball]] and [[cricket]]. 
# a turn at hitting a club at a ball.

